Dialogue: 0,0:00:-06.-35,0:00:-02.-76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world... Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:-02.-74,0:00:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world for you who seek freedom
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.09,0:00:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stretches out right before your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.26,0:00:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your endless dreams are your guide,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,surpass them, under the flag of your beliefs!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.44,0:00:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.95,0:00:26.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.45,0:00:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.62,0:00:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.97,0:00:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the summer sun\Nsways the sails of my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the cue to open the door to a new world
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.58,0:01:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing through the rocky waves of despair
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We head beyond the horizon
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.26,0:01:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making a splash,\NI've just started on my search
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.94,0:01:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heading towards a world without end
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.44,0:01:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart bursting with enthusiasm,\NI'll go to the ends of the earth
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.61,0:01:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In search of light yet unseen
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.90,0:01:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1,867... 1,868...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1,869...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Look!\N--Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.79,0:02:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! I've got something, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.50,0:02:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is big! This could be\Nthe guardian fish for this area!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.74,0:02:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.02,0:02:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Guardian fish...?\N--We can't eat that at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.59,0:02:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Shut up! You haven't even caught\Na single fish yet! Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.53,0:02:55.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then. Just watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:02:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna catch a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.97,0:03:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you catch any?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.14,0:03:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I will somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you a tropical juice\Nthat's great for your beauty
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.82,0:03:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and makes your skin smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.65,0:03:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want some, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.19,0:03:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smooth skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.56,0:03:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... what do you want smooth skin for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To get cuter!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind's fine. The current is fine, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.20,0:03:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like we won't\Nhave any problems today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.94,0:03:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's taken the bait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.12,0:03:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.69,0:03:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! What'd you catch?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:05.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Uprising of the Navigator!\NFor the Unyielding Dream!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a huge turban shell!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's not actually a turban shell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.24,0:04:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if this is edible...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna eat it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.75,0:04:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe cook it in its shell?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.22,0:04:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh... Boy, I thought I'd die! Hi, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who... are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.93,0:04:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Pardon me for not\Nintroducing myself sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a single call, I'll cordially\Ndeliver products to your town.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.38,0:04:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rice Rice from\NTransponder Snail Mail-Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.08,0:04:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transponder Snail Mail-Order? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.09,0:05:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I was in the process of\Nmaking a delivery with the Escar,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I got caught in a heavy storm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and got shipwrecked with the\Nwaves throwing me to and fro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I see...\N--You must've been shaken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shaken and stirred.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding. You're quite clever, Miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, drink some water.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.11,0:05:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.01,0:05:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't much, but as a token of my\Ngratitude, I'll give you these catalogues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With a single call, I'll deliver\Nthe products to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.92,0:05:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's convenient. So you'll\Ndeliver even when we're on the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.59,0:05:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.56,0:05:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.66,0:05:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Our motto is safe, reliable and cheap.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.53,0:05:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--And our mission is...\N--It's quite roomy inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our company is, believe it or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ahh! What're you guys doing?!\N--Wh-What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! This is what I'm going\Nto introduce to you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.71,0:05:55.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Buru Buru Blade, which is\Nfamiliar to people by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Buru Buru Blade is our\Ncompany's top product.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And today, I'll introduce\Nyou to this new model!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that many of you are already\Nusing the old Buru Buru Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the old model didn't, well, let you\Nchange the weight load, which was bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.77,0:06:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was fine for fathers, but many wanted\Nsmall children to be able to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.44,0:06:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I don't know what it is, but it looks fun!\N--So, this new model lets you\Nkeep a certain rhythm and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.68,0:06:32.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know all about this one, right?!\NThis is the Abu Abu Slider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our company's No. 1 product!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.05,0:06:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A new model has been\Nreleased! Give this a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.99,0:06:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--How is "top" different from "No. 1"?\N--Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, this is our best-selling\Nproduct! The "Golden Fish"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is recommended for people\Nwho don't exercise much these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll offer these great weight loss\Nproducts together as a set!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, today only, I'll also add
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20 bottles of plenty sweet Mero Mero\NJuice made in the West Blue,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a 26-volume encyclopedia set\Nthat will definitely be useful,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.75,0:07:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a pair of binoculars that are\Nconvenient for various things!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.08,0:07:08.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you think all this would cost?!\NA pretty penny, to be sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today only, I present this as a token\Nof my gratitude for saving my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna give them to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about 23,800 Berries?!\NJust take them, you thieves!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.47,0:07:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're selling them...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.43,0:07:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.47,0:07:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You wanna buy them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You carry kitchen knives, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! You're talking about this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.85,0:07:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is one of the high-quality items\Nproduced individually and carefully
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.75,0:07:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by a craftsman in High Mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this elasticity. And its\Nexcellent sharpness will last forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A dozen table knives,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.99,0:07:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pair of all-purpose kitchen\Nscissors that can cut anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a paring knife, and an electric\Nwhetstone! I'll add all these!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.43,0:07:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you act now, it's 2,980 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.67,0:07:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, Miss, here is a Smooth Skin Soap!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.24,0:08:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can make your skin as smooth as an egg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You do have everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. From mineral water to cannonballs,\Nthere's nothing we don't carry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.48,0:08:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have living things, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have what we don't carry, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.29,0:08:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you have paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Paper?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Strong paper\Nthat's big and hard to tear,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.89,0:08:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so that it'll take more than a\Nsmall sea breeze to get damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Transponder Snail Mail-Order\Npresents with confidence
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.01,0:08:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the best paper, A-Thousand-Year Paper!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.61,0:08:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Thousand-Year Paper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Thousand-Year Paper is manufactured\Nby using the A-Thousand-Year Tree
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.24,0:08:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that naturally grows on Eight-Nine Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This paper keeps away bugs,\Nand it's said that it won't fade
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.75,0:08:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for at least a thousand years,\Neven if it's kept exposed to the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.32,0:08:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the best for writing family\Ntrees or drawing treasure maps.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.12,0:08:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paper airplanes, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh...? That would be a waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.86,0:08:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.60,0:09:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You're gonna buy it?!\N--Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.53,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I caught her purchasing desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take it she's the type that price is\Nno object once she decides to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll just stir up her urge to buy as\Nmuch as possible and jack up the price.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:16.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you're interested... it's a\Nvaluable item in short supply...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you order now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if it'll be available\Nin five years... or ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't there some way you could\Nsell it to me? I'll pay any price.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nami who would rather\Ncount money than eat her meals...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nami who is a money monger...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...will pay any price?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're going too far...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then... If you insist that much...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ream of 1,000 A-Thousand-Year Papers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.08,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,normally costs 60 million Berries, but\Nhow about a special price of 48 million?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.59,0:09:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,48 million Berries...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:10:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that it costs\N48,000 Berries a sheet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you drop the price a little more?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:06.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll make it a lot cheaper...\NHow about 47.5 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.90,0:10:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--2 million Berries!\N--4.8 million Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--This sounds fishy...\N--Can't you go cheaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll buy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.64,0:10:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.98,0:10:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if we hand him over to the Navy,\Nwe'll have that and change.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.55,0:10:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Luffy. This is for Nami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...? Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy... You mean... that Monkey D. Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.43,0:10:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Sanji! Whatever, just untie me.\N--No, I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:49.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That odious pirate with\Na 100 million-Berry bounty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.41,0:10:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Monkey D. Luffy...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.51,0:10:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it... that's a pirate flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I missed\Nsuch important details!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.32,0:11:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I said untie me!\N--No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.65,0:11:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhm...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just remembered that I have\Nan important appointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.03,0:11:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.39,0:11:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Thanks for everything!\N--Hey, you forgot something...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.17,0:11:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he was scared of you...\NWanted man, Monkey D. Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.12,0:11:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. I'm going to work now,\Nso don't interrupt me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.25,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean "work"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.99,0:11:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:42.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not cute, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me! I won't let anyone near\Nyou until you're done with the work.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.10,0:11:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... what if the wind direction\Nsuddenly changes or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.27,0:11:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. Those clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't move, we'll have a fine\Nday today and there'll be no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.21,0:12:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come get me only when something\Nchanges with those clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.18,0:12:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.99,0:12:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things have been hectic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I haven't had free time since\Nwe entered the Grand Line, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Little Garden...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drum Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alabasta...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've written down all\Nthe routes that we took.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.81,0:12:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've stolen... no, obtained maps of the\Nsurrounding areas from towns as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll draw... my own world map...\Nmy dream since childhood...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! We'll make the deck spick-and-span\Nwhile Nami-san's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.61,0:13:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.18,0:13:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna do it, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.01,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--You traitor!\N--No fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That's right!\N--Then what about that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous! She's a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid! It doesn't matter\Nif it's a man or woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just help us, Moss-Head monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.66,0:13:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha ha, very funny,\NLove-Love Machine goblin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.07,0:13:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just help us, or I'll beat\Nyou up, you bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead. You think you\Ncan beat the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.27,0:13:36.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You say that because you\Ndon't know my goblin power.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.74,0:13:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.02,0:13:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll cut you down!\N--Want me to gut you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut you into pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Go! Fight! Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.03,0:13:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stop it, both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Don't just stand there and\Nwatch. Let's stop them already..
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ridiculous!\NDon't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.14,0:14:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know there's no way I can stop them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.40,0:14:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't I tell you to be quiet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mellorine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.32,0:14:23.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just one hit...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Pete's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.36,0:14:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bellemere-san... Bellemere-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Bellemere-san...\N--Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where does the wind come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.91,0:14:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--From the sea.\N--Sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. The wind born on the sea
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,brings blessings by blowing\Non Cocoyashi Village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just wind. The rain, clouds, rainbows...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.89,0:14:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything comes from the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.66,0:15:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Say... then where\Ndoes the sea come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:02.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Nami.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give Bellemere-san such a hard time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... Nojiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.83,0:15:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, you really are a curious girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...! Nami!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you did it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lady at the bookshop\Nstormed into the house in a rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.95,0:15:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go home. The dinner is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.66,0:15:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Bellemere-san...\NWhat's beyond that sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.39,0:15:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? I don't know what\Nlies beyond the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you were a marine?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.57,0:15:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was, but the sea is too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see... what's beyond the sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami...\N--I wonder if I can go beyond that sea...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a strong child. If you really want,\Nyou can go anywhere you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:15:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna use my navigation skills\Nto travel to all the world's oceans
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.96,0:16:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and make a world map of\Neverything I see. I sure will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.83,0:16:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I definitely will... some day...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.03,0:16:18.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will complete my own world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.04,0:16:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Luffy! Watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:26.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoopie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.51,0:16:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.78,0:16:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Amazing! Amazing!\N--Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.58,0:16:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... You've been working hard.\NAre you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... But what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.99,0:16:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what're you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.33,0:16:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.46,0:16:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is pretty fun. Wanna do it, too, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.43,0:16:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? It's noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The Smooth Skin Soap?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.57,0:16:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:17:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay! No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.15,0:17:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That idiot!\N--Gum-Gum...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.89,0:17:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bungee... Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:15.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out, Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.43,0:17:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.34,0:17:27.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! My map...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.64,0:17:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you were drawing a map?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.44,0:17:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.74,0:17:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what your "work" was...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's the only map in\Nthe world that recorded our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.68,0:17:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after entering the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.82,0:17:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My dream is to complete\Nmy own world map!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.03,0:17:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--But...\N--Just leave...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.43,0:17:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.57,0:17:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.50,0:18:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If "sorry" were enough,\Nthere'd be no need for the Navy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, leave already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.21,0:18:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, you'll be fined 100,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.25,0:18:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's your fault.\N--Why's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Well, I think so, too.\N--I think so, too.\N--Seriously, those guys
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! You, too?!\N--Now, Luffy, cheer up.\N--always get in my way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:24.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Smells like rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:19:00.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem! Luffy! Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem! The clouds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.77,0:19:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiders have ten legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.30,0:19:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, they have eight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that doesn't matter! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.31,0:19:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Centipedes have 100 legs...\N--Usopp! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.78,0:19:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Zoro! Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fined 100,000 Berries!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh... What should I do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.83,0:19:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do say so myself, this is perfect!\NAm I a genius or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.97,0:19:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.01,0:19:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.91,0:19:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Nami!\N--Hey! What were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me\Nbefore it got this bad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.85,0:19:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because... you said we'd\Nbe fined 100,000 Berries...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.79,0:19:58.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! How long are\Nyou gonna keep sleeping?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.26,0:20:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It's a tornado! It's a tornado!\N--It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Luffy! Zoro! Fold the sails!\N--Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.50,0:20:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Chopper! Secure the\Nstuff on the deck using ropes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji-kun! Turn to starboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.65,0:20:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umph!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.58,0:20:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Point the bow of the ship away from the\Ntornado, or we're gonna get swallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, hey...\N--Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If my precious map gets washed\Naway by waves or something,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.50,0:20:46.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll all pay... dearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is scary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.32,0:20:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The atmospheric pressure has risen\Nand the rain has stopped, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.88,0:21:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for your work. You can rest now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.79,0:21:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll go back to work,\Nso watch the clouds again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not done yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.43,0:21:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not! My goal is\Nto draw up the world map.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.23,0:21:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've just finished the first one.\NThe real work starts from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.97,0:21:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really going at it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.17,0:21:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like Nami-san that way, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there'll be a\N100,000-Berry fine again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.21,0:21:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.71,0:21:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been reading all this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, unfurl the sails!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full speed ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.82,0:21:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which direction should I run towards\Nto see a more wonderful tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.14,0:22:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took the helm and opened the\Nmiraculous map that I stored in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.92,0:22:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I aimed for the sky and sought out\Nmy dreams, though at times I got lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream; when I met you,\NI discovered the wonderful person in me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With just a bit of courage,\NI gained something grand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time for my "wish"\Nto become my "pledge"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.11,0:22:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's sketch out the tale of the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.15,0:22:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put all my feelings\Nin a brand new wind now
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.05,0:22:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shining ray! Find your brand new way
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.02,0:22:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A never-ending journey to be together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.19,0:22:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll chase after you\Nwherever you go, Shining ray
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.50,0:22:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Hey, do you know about the Navy's curry?\N--Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.77,0:23:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's famous. I hear that the chef on\Neach ship competes with all the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? That sounds yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.78,0:23:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The kid who fell from a Navy ship\Nearlier says he is a probationary cook.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It reminds me of my time\Nat the sea restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.75,0:23:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.15,0:23:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Recipe Handed Down!\NSanji, the Iron Man of Curry"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.46,0:23:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
